{"tid":2071900,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTuber爆料：iOS 將會改名，新名字為 iPhoneOS","createTime":"2020-06-20T07:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T06:48:06.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d16247386a3670ba3a56d3ace8fa0f11bf0a3837","tid":2071900,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"iOS 從此不再？著名 YouTuber 爆 WWDC20 內幕<br />\n虎仔 / 馬日山(uniqlo) 2020-06-19 11:58<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/216080/1/1/133121/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F216080%2F1%2F1%2F133121%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=f32b9c90\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/216080/1/1/133121/</a><br />\n<br />\nWWDC20 將會在美國時間 6 月 22 日揭幕，這個一年一度的 Apple 開發者大會，除了預計有新硬件產品發表，亦會有很多系統和軟件相關的新消息公佈。著名 YouTuber Jon Prosser 近期成為爆料界紅人，因為他不時透過 YouTube 或 Twitter 透露 Apple 的秘密。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-06/19/216080/uniqlo_1_798fe66fca2b3427db583e0597d2dac6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-06%2F19%2F216080%2Funiqlo_1_798fe66fca2b3427db583e0597d2dac6.jpg&h=1b91d528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS 從此不再？著名 YouTuber 爆 WWDC20 內幕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日他就暗示 iOS 將會改名，新名字為 iPhoneOS，現時我們無法估計 Prosser 的爆料是否正確，但 Apple 近年的確將一眾系統的名字統一化，並且以產品的名字直接命名，例如 macOS、tvOS、watchOS。Apple 亦將 iPadOS 從 iOS 分拆出來，如果 iOS 改名 iPhoneOS，這正正符合 Apple 的系統命名手法。<br />\n<br />\niOS 從此不再？著名 YouTuber 爆 WWDC20 內幕<br />\n<br />\n假如 Prosser 的說法屬實，Apple 可能會在 WWDC20 正式公佈 iOS 14 時一併宣佈；如果 iOS 真的改名 iPhoneOS，是否亦意味使用 iOS 的 iPod touch 會停產？相信下星期就有答案。"},{"pid":"99e27ad1f17f880d4ae326e537d54b05a0bf4eb0","tid":2071900,"uid":43369,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"都係Ios"},{"pid":"93989f3df0f1a8280f4139fc27a1b8b0ee6e11fe","tid":2071900,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99e27ad1f17f880d4ae326e537d54b05a0bf4eb0","tid":2071900,"uid":43369,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"都係Ios"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"瘋OS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6691c3142792aaad7bd2260f4865f6371a5c32c5","tid":2071900,"uid":239086,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"回歸初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd50b3cda3803b1914206e3ab41407131c84e90f","tid":2071900,"uid":37860,"like":1,"dislike":52,"score":-51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:59:52.000Z","msg":"咁有無IpadOS"},{"pid":"bca2490b0269ca19dd65a66688fbe240b3c2a374","tid":2071900,"uid":28114,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"dd50b3cda3803b1914206e3ab41407131c84e90f","tid":2071900,"uid":37860,"like":1,"dislike":52,"score":-51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:59:52.000Z","msg":"咁有無IpadOS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"一早改咗，瞓咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"229ec3c1511f83aad595d649cc01763b0716fb17","tid":2071900,"uid":235391,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"dd50b3cda3803b1914206e3ab41407131c84e90f","tid":2071900,"uid":37860,"like":1,"dislike":52,"score":-51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:59:52.000Z","msg":"咁有無IpadOS"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk/ipados/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fipados%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=c79e1f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk/ipados/</a><br />\n<br />\n坐左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji